	dprr:hasNoteText "His title is not preserved. He commanded the center of Octavian's fleet at Actium (Plut. Ant. 66.3; Vell. 2.85.2, the left wing; cf. Gardthausen 1.379; 2.198, note 36). See PIR² 1.220, no. 1129; De Laet no. 46." .
